<plot>High School football in small towns all across America can bring a community together, and in some cases, pit one community against another. The Rivals is the story of two towns in Maine, a stagnant mill town to the north and an affluent suburb along the southern coast. A story about the pride of place, the passion of tradition and the careful balance between success and respect.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?587162</url></doc>
